Title: boy pablo
Description: boy pablo is the indie pop music project of Chilean–Norwegian singer songwriter Nicolas Muñoz.

Title: pocky
Description: pocky is a snack food consisting of chocolate-coated biscuit sticks. It was named after the Japanese onomatopoetic word pokkin.

Title: mangas
Description: mangas are comics or graphic novels originating from Japan. The term manga is used in Japan to refer to both comics and cartooning.
